27:03.856 --> 27:06.458
Okay, ready?
One, two, three...

27:06.526 --> 27:08.560
Marion Cotillard. Yes!
Marion Cotillard. Oh, my God, stop it!

27:08.628 --> 27:09.928
Yes, I know. She's amazing!

27:09.996 --> 27:11.396
Amazing! Amazing!

27:11.464 --> 27:13.198
Amazing.
Gay!

27:13.266 --> 27:14.833
Gay! Gay. Gay, gay, gay.

27:14.901 --> 27:16.668
Gay, gay, gay, gay, gay, gay, gay.

27:16.736 --> 27:19.738
Oh, my gosh, I open my mouth
and a little purse falls out!

27:19.805 --> 27:20.605
That's so gay.

27:20.673 --> 27:21.973
How did that get in there?

27:22.041 --> 27:22.941
Mercedes?

27:24.571 --> 27:26.684
Mercedes?
I was just talking

27:26.685 --> 27:29.307
