I'm a college football fan.

27:29.308 --> 27:30.326
I like sports, too, you know.

27:30.579 --> 27:32.447
Oh, way to break the stereotype.

27:32.515 --> 27:35.270
Excuse me. I know it's not on your menu,

27:35.271 --> 27:36.685
